{"success": true, "message": "Fetched question.", "data": {"showTimer": true, "showAttemptInsight": true, "playSounds": true, "dontShowCorrectAnswerImmediately": false, "_id": "64c0e80f6f5bfc7ab78aea3e", "classes": [], "exams": ["615d7713c52ffa3c944600e3"], "subjects": ["615d708dbd4a37c4058ee5a8"], "chapters": ["615d6fec2b295b085ab6eb8e"], "topics": [], "concepts": [], "previousYearPapers": [{"_id": "61a8bf0fc821b6514e527d7e", "title": "BITSAT 2020", "isVisible": true}], "position": 0, "type": "singleCorrect", "level": 2, "approximateTimeRequired": 90, "question": {"text": "The upper half of an inclined plane with inclination $\\phi$ is perfectlysmooth while the lower halfis rough. A body starting from rest at the top will again come to rest at the bottom if the coefficient of friction for the lower half is given by", "image": null}, "options": [{"id": "X9iso", "text": "$2 \\cos \\phi$", "isCorrect": false, "image": null}, {"id": "Wqcw8", "text": "$2 \\sin \\phi$", "isCorrect": false, "image": null}, {"id": "0lH6W", "text": "$\\tan \\phi$", "isCorrect": false, "image": null}, {"id": "sgpXm", "text": "$2 \\tan \\phi$", "isCorrect": true, "image": null}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "Acceleration of block while sliding down upper half $=\\mathrm{g} \\sin \\phi$\r\n\r\nretardation of block while sliding down lower half $=-(\\mathrm{g} \\sin \\phi-\\mu \\mathrm{g} \\cos \\phi)$\r\n\r\nFor the block to come to rest at the bottom, acceleration in I half = retardation in II half.\r\n\r\n$\\mathrm{g} \\sin \\phi=-(\\mathrm{g} \\sin \\phi-\\mu \\mathrm{g} \\cos \\phi)$\r\n\r\n$\\Rightarrow \\mu=2 \\tan \\phi$\r\n\r\nAlternative method: According to work-energy theorem, $\\mathrm{W}=\\Delta \\mathrm{K}=0$\r\n\r\n(Since initial and final speeds are zero)\r\n\r\n$\\therefore$ Work done by friction $+$ Work done by gravity $=0$ i.e., $-(\\mu \\mathrm{mg} \\cos \\phi) \\frac{\\ell}{2}+\\mathrm{mg} \\ell \\sin \\phi=0$\r\n\r\nor $\\frac{\\mu}{2} \\cos \\phi=\\sin \\phi$ or $\\mu=2 \\tan \\phi$", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "numericalLowerLimit": null, "questionLabels": [], "__v": 0, "masterId": "MOGBSPYQ65145540", "bucket": "", "category": null, "microConcepts": [], "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText": null, "isRemoved": false, "cpyqbSubjects": ["61bb58181213731910ea0b70", "61c055eae8ce0dc8a5c62d33", "616057750283de43c87e3e1b", "61964fe0a5a5260118868021", "61964f81a5a526011886801d", "629f39e4ac11b26562e0625b", "616057920283de43c87e3e1e", "615f0c729476412f48314dab", "61a8a2c2e8ce0dc8a5c62d2d", "629105adee9e3ae00d63352b", "629f385f263330a77be9fa7d", "616056cd0283de43c87e3e15", "616057190283de43c87e3e18", "62962075e7f8e9ac4daeafd7", "64d50bd73df7f4a7f3017f6f", "66b79b34d4b564dfab4f94cc", "678ea9a09cc79e5f592bdc11", "67fa5fef4468eb1307ceb0ad", "6807d2ad647479b8e8696479"], "cpyqbChapters": ["616023b74026d68c120f2ba9", "616023b9c2e3bbfc3f2ecdd2", "616023b78dba43da23bef37e", "616023b542cfec4323be20b3", "61964c74ec1ca6c1a7365dcf", "61bb821fa52006d37a60e707", "61c089a30f62a0d239520145", "61964c76bae973f89e899882", "61e7bd7991a3d691658409aa", "616023b36f5a53c6a5d4ce42", "629f3a90cf4faea06a760897", "629109ec048d30f09d45ec7c", "629621223df2fbbc95bf297f", "629f390ce1a391b9376aa0de", "64eb06e13118f713ecfef1d7", "66d58567a75f05ee8564f723", "67921d641d5b5072da5e9aaa", "67fdff50378e1624ea7b6a0d", "680920323a10446a207fdf3e"], "cpyqbExams": ["61a8a124e8ce0dc8a5c62d2c"]}, "fetch_status": true}